{"tid":882432,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"盧柏迪古父轟皇馬賣C朗：偷走50球！","createTime":"2018-10-30T06:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T08:20:18.000Z","uid":5649,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bda0fb4b4bdd4f046bf20b89dd8b90a3958f1c6e","tid":882432,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:31:39.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=iDK3FfCBOU4dQZObA9%2Fo6TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=280c34a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】盧柏迪古被皇家馬德里辭退，在此之前，其父出言炮轟球會賣走基斯坦奴朗拿度，才是成績低迷的主因。<br />\n<br />\n「基斯坦奴朗拿度很好，每季都能攻入50球。現在沒有了他，沒有了一名主要射手，而且沒有引入新兵補充，傳過尼馬或其他球員，一個也沒有來，皇家馬德里根本從我兒子手上偷走了50球！」盧柏迪古（Julen Lopetegui）父親表示。<br />\n<br />\n盧柏迪古在今夏入主後，C朗就以1億歐元離隊加盟祖雲達斯，結果皇馬一沉不起，進攻啞火，現時於西甲以10戰14分排在第9位，落後榜首巴塞隆拿多達7分，前者就成為了眾矢之的。<br />\n<br />\n盧父指到現時為止，盧柏迪古仍然沒有說過任何一位球員的壞話：「他很滿意麾下的球員，常常說『我有很好的人腳，他們付出所有』。可惜他沒有資源，本來有，但那人已離開了。」"},{"pid":"5d168c08c44c4f076c6b0a10b1c1fc945d92f3a6","tid":882432,"uid":111006,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/30/154433_aff4b9e3f3e2b520298bc631c06f7943.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F30%2F154433_aff4b9e3f3e2b520298bc631c06f7943.png&h=6c5c3080&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bac5286b0c23fa9f06b6fb46cef1bb73a7174fe9","tid":882432,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T07:53:02.000Z","msg":"佩狗落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa2eade7e76e3c2b131c75fa1e6fe3185500d37","tid":882432,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"賤種朗<br />\n聯賽: 78射7入球 (1球靠12碼)<br />\n歐聯: 5射0入球 1紅牌<br />\n合共8.43%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a